name: Electric Beach
description:
Created during a time when I was playing a lot of Death Stranding and thinking about the concept of "beaches" in the game. Beaches as liminal space between life and death, beaches as collective consciousness and timelessness. Common to all yet unique for each human. "Electric Beach" is the fabric of my own unique beach. This is what it looks like. Come visit. 

Created with analog and digital processes. Video feedback, CRT rescans, and virtual reality drawings all merged into one. 

3360 x 1837 pixels
